data.description: Looking for a house with plenty of space? Then look no further. Conveniently located on a beautiful pond, in Liberty Hall Plantation. This six bedroom house has one bedroom downstairs that would be perfect for an office or workout room. Upstairs there is a great room that is perfect for a second living room or theater room. The master closet is very spacious as well. Brand new flooring  and paint throughout the entire house.
